in insurance 
melvin hanson cofounder of just sweats of columbus ohio his 
partner john barrett hawkins and dr richard pryde boggs of 
glendale were charged friday with murder conspiracy and insurance 
fraud 
the three are accused in the death of ellis henry greene 32 
whose body was found in boggs office last april 16 and was 
initially identified as hanson 
boggs told police he believed the body was that of hanson he 
said the man died after complaining of chest pains and hawkins had 
the body cremated the next day 
