did not match the one on hansons california drivers license the 
body subsequently was identified as greene a former ohioan 
a felony complaint issued by the los angeles district attorneys 
office traces the trios activities over a threeyear period the 
scheme allegedly began with hansons applications for multiple life 
insurance policies in 1986 
hanson signed a will in 1987 leaving all his property to hawkins 
upon his death hansons will directed that his body be cremated and 
that none of his relatives be notified according to court documents 
in january 1988 the complaint said hanson rented a miami 
condominium using an alias and the next month consulted a plastic 
surgeon about changing his appearance 
hanson on april 15 flew from miami to los angeles where he and 
boggs killed greene the next day the complaint alleges 
hanson left los angeles the same day using the name wolfgang von 
snowden and hawkins flew to los angeles to claim the body 
identified as hansons 
hawkins began filing claims for payments of death benefits on 
hanson two weeks later according to the court record 
hanson underwent cosmetic surgery to disguise his appearance a 
month after the slaying and began using the name and identification 
of the victim greene as well as the name von snowden hawkins went 
to colorado authorities said where he used the name jerry anthony 
greene 
records of telephone calls among hawkins hanson and boggs dating 
to december 1987 helped authorities uncover the alleged conspiracy 
