because of a lack of funds thousands packed bus stations and 
airports to enjoy the festival in other cities 
in rio however little seemed able to dampen carnival euphoria 
not last years record 1000 percent inflation nor charges of 
corruption and nepotism in the government nor the closing of 
schools and hospitals because city employees hadnt received their 
december paychecks 
